                      "x":  158,
                      "y":  1881,
                      "width":  500,
                      "height":  240,
                      "text":  "[飞书图片节点]\nToken: Hi4qbZmSjoz2e9xNPoFcrQ9fndf"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_d1_12",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  158,
                      "y":  1881,
                      "width":  500,
                      "height":  225,
                      "text":  "[飞书图片节点]\nToken: DPOlbmlk5oUFjVxrvK6cLCrznNH"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_86",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  202,
                      "width":  362,
                      "height":  124,
                      "text":  "层次结构\n分层目的：解决存储容量、价格、存储速度之间的矛盾\n速度快的存储器价格贵，容量小\n价格低的存储器速度慢，容量大",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_87",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  664,
                      "y":  100,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  102,
                      "text":  "CPU内\n寄存器\ncache",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_88",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  664,
                      "y":  185,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  102,
                      "text":  "主板内\ncache\n主存储器",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_89",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  664,
                      "y":  270,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "主板外\n磁盘、光盘",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_90",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  664,
                      "y":  334,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "离线\n磁带",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_91",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  433,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "二级存储系统",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_92",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  402,
                      "y":  415,
                      "width":  212,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "内存：CPU能直接访问的存储器",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_93",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  402,
                      "y":  451,
                      "width":  604,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "外存（辅存）：CPU不能直接访问的存储器。解决存储容量问题，以满足计算机的大容量需求。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_94",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  793,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "三级存储系统",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_95",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  402,
                      "y":  503,
                      "width":  418,
                      "height":  124,
                      "text":  "cache\n高速缓存（cache）：比其他内存速度更快容量更小的存储器。\n目的是提高访问速度，使主存存取速度和CPU运算速度相匹配。\n可分成L1cache、L2cache、L3cache。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_96",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  402,
                      "y":  752,
                      "width":  530,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "主存：除了cache之外的其他常规内存。用来存放系统运行期间的大量程序和数据。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_97",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  402,
                      "y":  1048,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "外存",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_98",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  1101,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  208,
                      "text":  "存储系统层次",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_99",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  818,
                      "y":  1172,
                      "width":  147,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "缓存-主存层次：内存",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_100",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  818,
                      "y":  1209,
                      "width":  147,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "主存-辅存层次：虚存",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_101",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  992,
                      "y":  634,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "存储地址分配",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_102",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1152,
                      "y":  608,
                      "width":  486,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "字节存储单元：存放一个字节（1B=8bit）的单元，相应的地址成为字节地址",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_103",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1152,
                      "y":  645,
                      "width":  524,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "字存储单元：存放一个机器字（1W=nB）的存储单元，相应的单元地址叫字地址。\n双字存储单元：存放两个机器字的存储单元，相应的单元地址叫双字地址",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_104",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  992,
                      "y":  871,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "性能指标",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_105",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1124,
                      "y":  709,
                      "width":  453,
                      "height":  124,
                      "text":  "存储容量\n指一个存储器中可以容纳的信息比特数，如KB、MB、GB、TB。\n可表示为：存储字数（存储单元数）*存储字长（每单元的比特数）。\n如1M*1bit、128K*8bit、512K*4bit。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_106",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1124,
                      "y":  814,
                      "width":  269,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "存取时间（存储器访问时间）\n指一次读/写操作命令发出到该操作完成",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_107",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1124,
                      "y":  879,
                      "width":  614,
                      "height":  102,
                      "text":  "存储周期\n指存储器连续读写过程中一次完整的存取操作所需的时间，CPU连续两次访问存储器的最小时间间隔。通常，存储周期略大于存取时间。\n存储周期=存取时间+线路恢复时间",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_108",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1124,
                      "y":  984,
                      "width":  488,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "存储器带宽\n单位时间里存储器所存取的信息量，通常以bit/s、B/s或者MB/s做度量单位",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_109",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  1910,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "半导体存储芯片",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_110",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  416,
                      "y":  1518,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  285,
                      "text":  "RAM（random access memory，随机读写存储器）\n掉电丢失数据，随机读写，速度比ROM快",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_111",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  416,
                      "y":  2148,
                      "width":  321,
                      "height":  102,
                      "text":  "ROM(read only memory，只读存储器)\n掉电不丢失数据，只能读不能写，速度比RAM慢\nROM-\u003ePROM-\u003eEPROM-\u003eE2PROM-\u003eFlash",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_112",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  992,
                      "y":  1333,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  311,
                      "text":  "SRAM（static RAM，静态RAM）\n存储位元是很多门电路组成的锁存器（触发器）",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_113",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  992,
                      "y":  1652,
                      "width":  572,
                      "height":  362,
                      "text":  "DRAM（dynamic RAM，动态RAM）\n存储位元是一个MOS管和一个电容，增加了行地址锁存器和列地址锁存器\n实现地址线复用从而分时传送行列地址码，增加了刷新计数器实现读出后再生和定时刷新",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_114",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1624,
                      "y":  1819,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "刷新",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_115",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1728,
                      "y":  1681,
                      "width":  264,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "定义：对DRAM定期进行的全部重写过程",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_116",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1728,
                      "y":  1717,
                      "width":  572,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "原因：因电容泄露而引起的DRAM所需信息的衰减需要及时补充，因此安排了定期刷新操作",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_117",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1728,
                      "y":  1957,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "刷新方法",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_118",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1860,
                      "y":  1754,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  153,
                      "text":  "集中式\n在最大刷新间隔时间内，集中安排一段时间进行刷新，存在CPU访存死时间",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_119",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1860,
                      "y":  1914,
                      "width":  395,
                      "height":  162,
                      "text":  "分散式\n在每个读/写周期之后插入一个刷新周期，无CPU访存死时间",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_120",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1860,
                      "y":  2084,
                      "width":  166,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "异步式\n集中式和分散式的折中",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_122",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  2380,
                      "width":  384,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "存储容量的扩展\n所需芯片数d=设计要求的存储器容量/选择芯片存储器容量",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_123",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  686,
                      "y":  2249,
                      "width":  614,
                      "height":  117,
                      "text":  "位扩展\n给定的芯片字长位数较短，需要在位数方向扩展（加大字长），而芯片的字数和存储器字数一致。\n位扩展连接方式：将个存储芯片地址线、片选线和读写控制线相应的并连起来公用，而将各芯片的数据线单独列出分开连接",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_124",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  686,
                      "y":  2375,
                      "width":  614,
                      "height":  102,
                      "text":  "字扩展\n给定芯片字数少，仅需要在字数方向扩展，而位数不变。\n字扩展方法：字扩展将芯片的地址线、数据线和读写控制线并联公用，由片选信号来区分各个芯片。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_125",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  686,
                      "y":  2480,
                      "width":  488,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "字位扩展\n给定的芯片字数和位数均不符合要求，需要先进行位扩展，再进行字扩展。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_126",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  2649,
                      "width":  142,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "提高访存速度的措施",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_127",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  444,
                      "y":  2560,
                      "width":  302,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "芯片技术：提高单个芯片的访问速度\n如突发传输技术，SDRAM技术，CDRAM技术",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_128",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  444,
                      "y":  2625,
                      "width":  530,
                      "height":  102,
                      "text":  "结构技术：改进存储器和CPU之间的连接方式\n如采用并行技术的双端口存储器（使用两套独立的读写电路，属于空间并行技术）\n多体交叉存储器（读芯片组模块时非顺序读而是交叉读，属于时间并行技术）",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_129",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  444,
                      "y":  2710,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "层次技术",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_130",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  3213,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "cache和虚存",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_131",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  398,
                      "y":  2974,
                      "width":  306,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "cache：解决CPU和主存之间的速度不匹配问题",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_132",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  764,
                      "y":  2762,
                      "width":  591,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "访存局部性：存储空间90%的访问局限于存储空间的10%的区域中，另外10%的访问则分布在90%的区域中。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_133",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  764,
                      "y":  2818,
                      "width":  604,
                      "height":  117,
                      "text":  "cache的基本原理\nCPU读取内存时，发出要读的字的内存地址到cache和内存，若cache命中，则直接从cache读出该字传送给CPU，若cache未命中，则把该字从主存读出送到CPU并同时送往cache。\n由于程序局部性原理，cache的命中率可接近于1，使得在性能上，内存的平均读出时间可接近cache的读出时间",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_134",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  764,
                      "y":  2944,
                      "width":  395,
                      "height":  80,
                      "text":  "cache命中率h=cache存取次数Nc/内存存取次数\n=cache存取次数Nc/（cache存取次数Nc+主存存取次数Nm）",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_135",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  764,
                      "y":  3000,
                      "width":  473,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "平均访问时间ta=命中率h*cache访问时间tc+(1-命中率h)*主存访问时间tm",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_136",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  764,
                      "y":  3037,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  307,
                      "text":  "访问效率e=cache访问时间tc/平均访问时间ta",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_137",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  242,
                      "y":  4024,
                      "width":  138,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "主存和cache的映射",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_138",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  440,
                      "y":  3630,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  262,
                      "text":  "全相联：主存的数据块可复制到cache的任意一行",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_139",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  440,
                      "y":  3900,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  277,
                      "text":  "直接相连：主存的数据块可复制到cache的固定某一行",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_140",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  440,
                      "y":  4184,
                      "width":  516,
                      "height":  283,
                      "text":  "组相联：主存的数据块可复制到cache的固定某一组的任意一行",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_141",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  398,
                      "y":  3452,
                      "width":  567,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "虚存：在主存和辅存之外附加一些硬件和软件实现，属于三级存储体系中的主存-辅存层次",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_142",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1025,
                      "y":  3352,
                      "width":  604,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "引入原因：CPU能直接访问的只有内存，因此程序只有先调入内存才能运行，而某些程序需要很大内存，物理内存不能满足程序需要",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_143",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1025,
                      "y":  3408,
                      "width":  604,
                      "height":  89,
                      "text":  "原理：程序运行时，给程序分配一定运行空间，把程序部分调入内存。当分配的内存不够，只调入当前正在运行或将要运行的程序块，其余部分继续驻留在辅存。这样程序的虚地址空间可以远大于实地址空间。基于局部性原理，当主存命中率很高，虚存访问时间可接近于主存访问时间。而虚存大小仅依赖于辅存大小。",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_144",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1025,
                      "y":  3542,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "分类",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_145",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1129,
                      "y":  3505,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "页式虚存",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_146",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1129,
                      "y":  3542,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "段式虚存",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  },
                  {
                      "id":  "n_z1_147",
                      "type":  "text",
                      "x":  1129,
                      "y":  3578,
                      "width":  120,
                      "height":  60,
                      "text":  "段页式虚存",
                      "color":  "#5178c6"
                  }
              ],
